datasets/
    * Input (pots/ and LAMMPS input) files common across multiple implementations kept here

baselie/
    * Baseline MPI+OpenMP implementations

refactored/
    * Refactored (OCR, CnC, etc.) implementations go here


##########################################################
To build and run the apps using unified run-system
##########################################################

1. Source compiler paths and the environment variables/paths needed for the unified run-system
    $ source ../apps_env.bash

2. Navigate to "build_and_run/" directory for a given implementation. E.g.,
    $ cd baseline/mpi-serial/doe-original/build_and_run/

3. Go to any subdirectory listed under build_and_run/. E.g.,
    $ cd serial/
    or
    $ cd mpi/

4. Call the "run_app" script with appropriate problem size arguments
    $ run_app #For help
    $ run_app ss_small 10 #run the app with "small" problem size for 10 iterations

